myHQAreaMetaData.about:
myHQ offers meeting rooms in Hyderabad for your or your team's requirements to conduct meetings, presentations, interviews and many more.


Hold your client meetings, workshops or get your team to present in our fully-serviced meeting rooms. Book on-demand by the hour, and ensure your meeting runs smoothly.

We'll help you find the ideal meeting room to host an event, to interview candidates, or a space to conduct training sessions. You will find many meeting rooms equipped with Projector / Screen to ensure seamless connectivity. simply choose a meeting room with myHQ in Hyderabad and get instant confirmation.
